    "Explainable AI (XAI) can play a vital role in this domain by increasing transparency and explainability within attack systems, allowing for a better understanding of LLM vulnerabilities.",
    "Developing XAI techniques to enhance the interpretability of LLM vulnerabilities is another essential research direction for advancing the security and privacy of LLMs.",
    "Existing Defense Mechanisms, Challenges, and Future Research Direction: To mitigate vulnerabilities posed by security and privacy attacks, various defense techniques have been proposed in existing research.",
    "Instruction defense [219], paraphrasing [104], and re-tokenization [104] methods are commonly employed to defend against prompt injection attacks.",
    "To defense jailbreaking attacks, SmoothLLM [215], LLM Guard [6], and perplexity filtering [78] are widely used."
